# TIP: provider keys (fal / OpenAI / Anthropic / Pexels / Wispr) can also be set
# from the Studio UI — header → "· keys" — at runtime, per user, encrypted, no
# restart needed. Env vars here act as the instance-wide defaults.

# VOICE-OVER (open-source, self-hosted — VoxCPM-2). Run workers/voice, then set this.
# When set, Forgecast prefers self-hosted VoxCPM-2 over cloud fal TTS. See workers/voice/README.md.
VOXCPM_URL=
# (Cloud fallback for voice-over if VOXCPM_URL is unset: fal TTS via FAL_KEY_VOICE ?? FAL_KEY)
#
# KEYLESS voice-over (the default on the Cloudflare deploy): MeloTTS via Workers AI —
# free daily neuron allowance (~9 hours of audio/day), no key. On the deploy it uses
# the Worker's AI binding automatically; off-Workers it activates with:
# CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
# CLOUDFLARE_AI_API_TOKEN=
# CF_AI_TTS_MODEL=@cf/myshell-ai/melotts   # optional override
# Pin a specific voice provider regardless of the default order (voxcpm | fal-tts | cloudflare):
# FORGECAST_VOICE_PROVIDER=

# Image generation via fal.ai
FAL_KEY=
# Or generate images FREE on a self-hosted Stable Diffusion WebUI (Automatic1111,
# https://github.com/AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui — launch it with --api).
# Then call generate-image with provider="stablediffusion". No fal key, no per-use cost.
# SD_WEBUI_URL=http://localhost:7860
# SD_STEPS=25            # optional
# SD_CFG_SCALE=7         # optional

# Video generation via fal.ai (set this to enable the Video tab)
FAL_KEY_VIDEO=
# Or generate video FREE with open models (LTX-Video, Wan) on Hugging Face ZeroGPU
# Spaces — a FREE HF account token gives you your own daily GPU quota (~5 min/day):
# https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens  (also settable per-user in Studio → keys)
# HF_TOKEN=
# HF_SPACE=ltx-video-distilled     # optional — pin a catalog space
# HF_SPACES_ALLOW_ANON=1           # self-host only: call Spaces anonymously (per-IP quota)
# NOTE: Cloudflare Workers AI video (CF_AI_VIDEO_MODEL) is PARTNER-BILLED — every CF
# video model costs money (unlike keyless FLUX images). Set it only with billing enabled.
# CF_AI_VIDEO_MODEL=

# ── Agent brain (the tool-calling "Agent" — PLAN / AUTO-RUN) ──────────────────
# OpenAI is the default for now.
OPENAI_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini          # optional override
#
# To switch the agent to Claude instead, set FORGECAST_AGENT_LLM=anthropic and add
# an ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (https://console.anthropic.com). The Claude adapter is in
# place and ready — it's just opt-in.
# FORGECAST_AGENT_LLM=anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8   # optional override (defaults to Claude Opus 4.8)
#
# Or run a FREE, self-hosted local model via Ollama (https://github.com/ollama/ollama) —
# no key, no per-use cost. `ollama serve`, `ollama pull llama3.1`, then:
# FORGECAST_AGENT_LLM=ollama
# OLLAMA_URL=http://localhost:11434     # optional (default)
# OLLAMA_MODEL=llama3.1                 # optional (any model you've pulled)

# Content guardrails (optional). Every prompt/brief/script is checked before
# generation; sexual content involving minors is always hard-blocked. Add your own
# policy/brand-unsafe terms here (comma-separated, matched on word boundaries).
# CONTENT_BLOCKLIST=competitorbrand, some-slur, another-term

# Durable persistence (optional — omit both for ephemeral in-memory)
# FORGECAST_DB=./.forgecast/forgecast.db
# FORGECAST_DATA_DIR=./.forgecast/objects

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# VOICE INPUT  (talk into the agent chat box — Wispr Flow speech-to-text)
# Get a key at https://wisprflow.ai/developers
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WISPRFLOW_API_KEY=
# FORGECAST_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3210

# Short-form video (optional — run the MoneyPrinter worker; see workers/shorts/README.md)
# FORGECAST_VIDEO_WORKER_URL=http://localhost:8080

# Real-footage search (optional — find copyright-free stock video by topic, then import + montage).
# Get a free key at https://www.pexels.com/api/  (the same key the MoneyPrinter worker uses).
# PEXELS_API_KEY=

# ── Voice agent (Vapi phone/voice webhook — optional) ─────────────────────────
# Drive Forgecast by voice via a Vapi assistant whose Server URL points at
# <FORGECAST_BASE_URL>/api/voice/vapi. That webhook runs the agent (generate + PUBLISH),
# so it is FAIL-CLOSED: with VAPI_WEBHOOK_SECRET unset the webhook is DISABLED (503).
# Set it, and configure the SAME value as your Vapi assistant's server secret so Vapi
# sends it as the `x-vapi-secret` header; requests without the matching header get 401.
# VAPI_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# Optional — on a multi-user deploy, scope the assistant to one user's workspace by id
# (else it acts as the local operator):
# VAPI_OWNER=


# Deployment profile (optional — "local" default, or "baxter-cloud" for Cloudflare R2 asset storage)
# FORGECAST_PROFILE=baxter-cloud
# R2_ACCOUNT_ID=
# R2_BUCKET=
# R2_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
# R2_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
# R2_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=        # optional public bucket / CDN domain for serving objects
# R2_ENDPOINT=               # optional override (defaults to https://<R2_ACCOUNT_ID>.r2.cloudflarestorage.com)

# ── Publishing / Distribution ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Webhook publisher — cross-post to ANY endpoint (Zapier / Make / n8n / Slack /
# Discord / your own backend). The easiest way to wire up + verify cross-posting:
# Forgecast POSTs { source, content, channels, mediaUrls } to this URL.
# WEBHOOK_PUBLISH_URL=https://hooks.zapier.com/hooks/catch/xxx/yyy
# WEBHOOK_PUBLISH_SECRET=            # optional — sent as `Authorization: Bearer <secret>`

# OmniSocials aggregator (one key → 10+ platforms — the fast path)
# OMNISOCIALS_API_KEY=

# Instagram Graph API (requires IG Business Account + Meta App Review)
# INSTAGRAM_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# INSTAGRAM_IG_USER_ID=

# LinkedIn Posts API (requires Developer App + w_member_social scope)
# LINKEDIN_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# LINKEDIN_AUTHOR_URN=urn:li:person:xxxx

# YouTube Data API v3 (requires OAuth + youtube.upload scope)
# YOUTUBE_ACCESS_TOKEN=

# ── Ads: measure → optimize (optional) ────────────────────────────────────────
# The creative-fatigue + audit features work with NO keys — POST your metrics to
# /api/ads/audit (or pass `metrics` to the MCP tool). Set the keys below only to
# AUTO-PULL live metrics from a connected ad account.
#
# Meta (Facebook/Instagram) Marketing API — Insights edge
# META_ADS_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# META_ADS_ACCOUNT_ID=             # with or without the act_ prefix
# META_GRAPH_VERSION=v23.0         # optional (bump as Meta sunsets versions)
#
# Google Ads API — googleAds:searchStream (the OAuth refresh dance is yours to run)
# GOOGLE_ADS_DEVELOPER_TOKEN=
# GOOGLE_ADS_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# GOOGLE_ADS_CUSTOMER_ID=          # digits only
# GOOGLE_ADS_LOGIN_CUSTOMER_ID=    # optional — manager (MCC) account
# GOOGLE_ADS_API_VERSION=v21       # optional (bump as Google sunsets versions)

# ── Sign-in (Google OAuth) — for hosting Forgecast as a multi-user website ────
# Leave ALL of these unset for the default open, single-operator self-host mode.
# Setting all three turns on authentication end to end (sign-in page + sessions).
#  1. Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials → OAuth client (Web).
#  2. Authorized redirect URI:  <FORGECAST_BASE_URL>/api/auth/callback
#  3. AUTH_SECRET signs session cookies — use 32+ random bytes:
#       openssl rand -base64 32
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
# AUTH_SECRET=
# FORGECAST_BASE_URL must be the site's public origin (used for the OAuth redirect).

# ── Additional overrides (read in code; optional) ─────────────────────────────
# Video (BYO): non-fal video via Replicate, self-hosted SkyReels, or pin a provider.
# REPLICATE_API_TOKEN=
# REPLICATE_VIDEO_MODEL=          # optional (default minimax/video-01)
# SKYREELS_URL=                   # self-hosted SkyReels-V2 worker (workers/skyreels)
# FORGECAST_VIDEO_PROVIDER=       # pin: fal-video | replicate | skyreels | hf-spaces | cloudflare
#
# Montage renderer (Remotion worker on Fly.io — SET IN PROD; enables timeline/montage export).
# MONTAGE_WORKER_URL=https://forgecast-montage.fly.dev
#
# Model overrides for the keyless/BYO image providers.
# CF_AI_IMAGE_MODEL=@cf/black-forest-labs/flux-1-schnell   # keyless CF image model
# OPENAI_IMAGE_MODEL=gpt-image-1                            # non-fal OpenAI image model
#
# Alternate LLM/base-url overrides (advanced).
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=                # OpenAI-compatible gateway
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=
# OLLAMA_API_KEY=                 # if your Ollama endpoint requires a key
#
# Publisher API version pins (bump as platforms sunset versions).
# META_GRAPH_VERSION=v23.0        # Meta Graph (Instagram insights + publish)
# LINKEDIN_VERSION=202508         # LinkedIn versioned API (YYYYMM)
# GOOGLE_ADS_API_VERSION=v21      # Google Ads API
#
# Billing (Mollie — optional; per-user Pro entitlement is a known-deferred WIP).
# MOLLIE_API_KEY=
#
# Ops.
# ADMIN_EMAILS=you@example.com    # comma-separated; unlocks the /admin surface
# AGENT_REACH_ENABLED=            # optional Agent-Reach trends tool
# AGENT_REACH_BIN=
